		+ Gain 1 point in strength" .. NEXT_LEVEL .. "2 points in strength!" $) 1 lvl
	then;
		($ "+ Gain 1 point in fitness
		+ Gain 1 point in strength" .. NEXT_LEVEL .. "2 points in fitness!" $)
;

